    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "the problem is there is no \"stepping back\" to rest. it's not some temporary exhaustion. it's just the same pattern every single time. i've tried the rest, i've tried the therapy, i've tried starting over. nothing changes. it's just a loop that doesn't stop.",
